{"tid":1811133,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【和你Jam】1月6 號","createTime":"2020-01-04T12:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T15:34:10.000Z","uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dcc21f2cc2585aed3a192ad617dddd0635818fd","tid":1811133,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKgdzJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKgdzJ8.jpg&h=14a8c0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【和你Jam】<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年1月6日（星期一）<br />\n時間：下午12:00-3:00<br />\n地點：觀塘巧明街/駿業街Walking East 雕塑<br />\n<br />\n香港保險仝人職工會 + 香港音樂人工會 招募會員聯合街站<br />\n<br />\n12月罷工試過同 香港酒店工會 Hong Kong Hotel Employees Union一起開站；1月6號我地又出動啦！今次選擇中午和你Jam，重要同 香港保險㒰人職工會 Hong Kong Insurance Union一齊落區開街站！各位保險人音樂人，中午放飯落來啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港保險仝人職工會TG頻道（附設公海）：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkiunion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkiunion&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=8be8121c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkiunion</a><br />\n登記成為「香港保險仝人職工會」會員：<a href=\"https://cutt.ly/reTxKIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcutt.ly%2FreTxKIo&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=e472519c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cutt.ly/reTxKIo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港音樂人工會TG頻道（附設公海）：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKMuIN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKMuIN&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=7a43ad18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKMuIN</a><br />\n登記成為「香港音樂人工會」會員：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NBwQHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NBwQHE&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=e17f0566\" data-auto-link t